==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Coriaceous
<hw>Co`ri*a"ceous</hw> <pr>(k?`r?-?"sh?s)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>coriaceous</ets>, fr. <ets>corium</ets> leather. See
<er>Cuirass</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Consisting of or resembling,
leather; leatherlike; tough.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Stiff, like leather or
parchment.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coriander</ent>⟦br⟧
